snippet.title: My Anticipated Book Releases 2022 | Fantasy
snippet.description:
So Excited for all these books!

The Starless Crown by James Rollins
Daughter of the Moon Goddess by Sue Lynn Tan
The Amber Crown by Jacey Bedford
The Final Strife by Saara El Arifi
The City of Dusk by Tara Sim
Spear by Nicola Griffith
Engines of Empire by Mike Heath
The Justice of Kings by Lauren Panepinto
Scorpica by GR McAllister

Thank you all so much for watching! You! You right there are awesome! :)
